---
title: Falafel and Golden Rice Bowls with Chopped Salad and Tahini-Yogurt Drizzle
description: Golden turmeric and cumin add warming and wholesome flavour to fluffy basmati rice. Load up your bowl with crunchy salad, creamy tahini-yogurt drizzle, hearty falafels and briny feta.

